Third party system dependency: 
gpsd need to be installed as part of the dependency of gps_umd pacakge
1. At system-dependencies/gpsd-2.95
2. ./autogen.sh, make, then sudo make install

libserial-0.5.2 handles leaflabs_adc's serial communication
1. At system-dependencies/libserial-0.5.2
2. ./configure, then sudo make install

Use rosmake at smart-ros-pkg to compile all the included packages.
For compilation of individual package, a simple make command at the package folder is suffice for recompilation.
